 MAPLIA system is useful for policy decision support on air quality improvement strategies, and could be applied to other urban areas where AQP need to be implemented and monitored.";s:11:"article_ref";s:44:"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27348699";s:18:"article_viewscount";s:3:"208";s:17:"article_timestamp";s:19:"2018-05-06 20:34:51";s:14:"article_status";s:1:"1";}i:25;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:10:"article_id";s:3:"223";s:13:"article_title";s:270:"""สถานการณ์การจัดการมูลฝอยติดเชื้อ
